{"data":[{"id":559931228,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559931228","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545794641,"updated_time":1545794904,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e1月1号发证明过程。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看出来了，你无非就是想火一把。现在这流量的世道，美也好，丑也罢，只要哗众成功了，赚钱的机会就来了。相比较而言，用丑的一面博眼球更简单更容易。以前的什么凤姐，某手里的一些用户，都是这么起来的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我估计你的想法差不多就是这样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多少年前看的一篇名为“审丑”的文章，其实真的早就应验了。你如果选对了路，靠这个未必不能火一把。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是找哥猜这种东西想火，真是滑稽。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先关注这个的人虽然很多，但一般都是学术界的或者民科偏多，民科基本上不会搭理你，他们忙着用自己的方法证明呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e学术界的，除非你真的证出来了，不然，一份疑似民科的“证明“，不好意思，没人会搭理你的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没有得到权威承认的证明，大众根本不会关注，因为这种所谓的证明，真的是网上一搜一大把。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本身受众就小，加上太多的可重复性，这个话题压根没一点吸收流量的能力，营销号什么的也根本不会去带节奏，因为资本不会做这种明显亏本的生意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e客观来说，你这一套行动下来，也就用“一月一日发证明”这个造势的行为能勉强吸一点流量。但是也只能如此了，此事过后，说不定也能成个过千粉的“大V”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是没有其他产出，加上热闹看完了，估计粉慢慢也就掉完了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e综上，奉劝一句，你还是好好准备高考吧。将来如果真能在学术圈混了，再想着搞个大新闻也不迟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚看了一下你的主页，居然已经过千粉了，果然知乎现在韭菜确实好割。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e加油，争取过个万粉，我看好你呦！\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"1月1号发证明过程。。。看出来了，你无非就是想火一把。现在这流量的世道，美也好，丑也罢，只要哗众成功了，赚钱的机会就来了。相比较而言，用丑的一面博眼球更简单更容易。以前的什么凤姐，某手里的一些用户，都是这么起来的。我估计你的想法差不多就是这…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=494\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settin